Called the Messenger of the Gods and the Nimble, Hermod is a demigod of communication, freedom, luck, messengers, and thieves. He guides the souls of the dead to Niflheim and welcomes dead heroes to Asgard. He is chaotic neutral.
Sources: Deities &amp; Demigods (Third Edition), Dragon magazine #110 - "For Better or Norse: I", Gods, Demi-Gods &amp; Heroes